    "To address these problems thoroughly, this paper aims to unify a wide range of RS tasks and concentrates on constructing a largescale multi-modal dataset containing multi-sensor RS images based on diverse existing RS datasets.To leverage the robust generalization and emergent ability of large language models (LLMs), a versatile MLLM called EarthGPT is proposed for multi-sensor RS image comprehension, unifying various RS interpretation tasks effectively.",
